URL: https://www2.swift.com/mystandards/#/mp/mx/_PRnKMI0EEe6xfvjD11p3MQ/_PRnKMY0EEe6xfvjD11p3MQ
Description: The PaymentStatusTrackerUpdate message is sent by an agent to a tracking facility to monitor the progress of a business transaction, and to update the status of this business transaction for obtaining tracking and transparency purpose.

Usage:
Multiple business transaction statuses may be reported in a single message, and each status may include all relevant information of a single transaction or multiple transactions of the tracked payment(s) exchanged.


